        Stage 1 : Bet on card color between Red or Black\n
        Stage 2 : Bet on next card number Greater or Lower than your first card\n
        Stage 3 : Bet on next card number Inside or Outside the interval of your two first cards\n
        Stage 4 : Bet on next card suit between Hearts, Diamonds, Spades or Clubs\n
        Stage 5 : Bet on if you already have next card or not, based only on card values.\n

